org.researchstack.backbone.storage.file

Class PinCodeConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.researchstack.backbone.storage.file.PinCodeConfig

  • public class PinCodeConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows you to customize the type/strength of the pin code that the user must create to protect their data.
